# FILE: HomePage.desc
# ROLE: Master Layout & Landing Experience for HalabUnver Ecosystem
# THEME: Dark-only — #070C18 bg · #6366F1 accent · #8B5CF6 accent2
# STYLE: Glassmorphism cards · Gradient text · Dot-pattern bg · Fade-up animations

## DESIGN SYSTEM (Current)
- BACKGROUND: #070C18 (deep navy-black) — dark only, no light/dark toggle
- SURFACE: #0F1828 cards with 1px #1E2D45 borders and rounded-2xl/3xl
- ACCENT: #6366F1 (indigo) + #8B5CF6 (purple) gradient
- TYPOGRAPHY: IBM Plex Sans Arabic — RTL by default via html dir="rtl"
- ANIMATIONS: animate-fade-up, animate-blink-soft, gradient glow on scroll
- UTILITY CLASSES: gradient-text, gradient-bg, glass, dot-bg, section-label (Tailwind @utility)

## 1. HEADER (Sticky · Full-Width · Always Visible)
- BG: bg-[#070C18]/70 at top → bg-[#070C18]/95 + backdrop-blur-xl on scroll
- BORDER-BOTTOM: border-[#1E2D45]/40 at top → border-[#1E2D45] on scroll
- HEIGHT: 72px fixed
- LOGO: "ح" icon (gradient-bg rounded-xl) + "حلب يونيفر" text (gradient-text on "يونيفر")
- NAV LINKS (desktop): الأكاديمية · المكتبة · المستقلون · المتجر · لوحة التحكم
  - Each link has an emoji icon prefix
  - Active state: bg-[#6366F1]/15 + border border-[#6366F1]/25 + gradient underline dot
  - Hover: text-[#F1F5F9] + bg-white/5
- RIGHT ACTIONS:
  - Search icon button → opens full-screen search modal
  - الأخبار badge: bg-[#F43F5E]/10 · rose text · blinking dot · links to /exam-hub
  - دخول button: ghost style with login icon
  - انضم مجاناً: gradient-bg CTA button
- ACCOUNT-AWARE STATE (post-auth):
  - Guest: shows دخول + انضم مجاناً
  - Student: shows user avatar + name + dropdown (dashboard / logout)
  - Business: shows user avatar + "لوحة الأعمال" link + dropdown
  - Admin: shows user avatar + "لوحة الإدارة" link with special styling
- SEARCH MODAL: full-screen overlay bg-[#070C18]/92 + backdrop-blur-md
  - Input: bg-[#0F1828] with focus:border-[#6366F1]
  - Quick tag pills: المكتبة · الأكاديمية · المستقلون · المتجر

## 2. HERO SECTION
- BG: dot-bg pattern with 3 radial gradient glows (indigo · purple · teal)
- HEIGHT: min-h-[92vh] flex items-center justify-center
- BADGE: "المنصة الأكاديمية الأولى في حلب · إصدار 2026" — blinking green dot
- H1: "منصتك الأكاديمية" + gradient-text line "تعلّم · اكسب · ابنِ مستقبلك"
  - Font: font-black, text-7xl max, leading-[1.15]
- SUBTITLE: muted text, max-w-580px centered, 2 lines + accent sub-line
- CTAs: gradient-bg "ابدأ مجاناً" + ghost border "اعرف أكثر عن المنصة"
- TRUST BADGES: ✓ تسجيل مجاني · ✓ محتوى أكاديمي حقيقي · ✓ دفع آمن عبر ShamCash
- SCROLL INDICATOR: vertical gradient line + "SCROLL" text at bottom

## 3. STATS SECTION
- BG: bg-[#0F1828]/50 + border-y border-[#1E2D45]
- CENTERED HEADER: section-label "بالأرقام" + h2 + subtitle paragraph
- GRID: grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-5 with AnimatedCounter
- STAT CARDS: bg-[#0F1828] · rounded-2xl · emoji icon · colored value · muted label
- STATS: طالب مسجّل · مصدر في المكتبة · دورة أكاديمية · مستقل نشط · منتج في المتجر

## 4. PILLARS SECTION (4 Platform Cards)
- CENTERED HEADER: section-label "منصات المنظومة" + h2 + description
- GRID: grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 with gap-6/8
- CARD STYLE: rounded-3xl · colored bg tint · border-[#1E2D45]
  - Hover: border-[#6366F1]/30 + shadow-2xl
  - Each card: emoji icon box (accent bg) · title · description · stats row with accent dot
- 4 PILLARS: أكاديمية حلب (#6366F1) · مكتبة حلب (#14B8A6) · سوق المستقلين (#F59E0B) · متجر حلب (#F43F5E)

## 5. FEATURED OFFERS SECTION
- BG: bg-[#0F1828]/60 + border-y
- CENTERED HEADER: section-label "عروض المنصة" + h2 + description
- GRID: grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 — large course card (col-span-2) + 2 mini cards
- LARGE CARD: from-[#6366F1]/12 to-[#8B5CF6]/6 gradient · course badge · CTA
- MINI CARDS: store offer card + freelance CTA card

## 6. NEWS SECTION
- CENTERED HEADER: section-label "آخر الأخبار" + h2 + description
- LIST: space-y-4 news rows — date · title · colored tag pill
- FOOTER LINK: centered "عرض جميع الأخبار ←"

## 7. XP GAMIFICATION SECTION
- BG: bg-[#0F1828]/60 + border-y
- CENTERED HEADER: section-label "نظام نقاط الخبرة" + h2 + formula
- TWO-COLUMN GRID: XP actions list (left) + Profile preview card (right)
- XP LIST: bg-[#0F1828] rows with colored XP badge per action
- PROFILE CARD: avatar + name + level bar + 2x2 stats grid

## 8. CTA SECTION (Hero-Grade)
- FULL-BLEED: relative overflow-hidden with layered bg gradients + dot-bg + glows
- BADGE: blinking green dot + "التسجيل مجاني — انضم الآن"
- H2: text-7xl font-black "مستعد للانضمام؟"
- SUBTITLE: max-w-2xl centered
- CTAs: large gradient "ابدأ مجاناً — انضم الآن" + ghost "تواصل معنا"
- DIVIDER: gradient lines + "إحصائيات المنصة" label
- MINI STATS: 3-col grid of colored stats cards

## 9. FOOTER
- BG: bg-[#070C18] + border-t border-[#1E2D45]
- GRID: 4 columns — Brand · التطبيقات · المنصة · تواصل معنا
- BRAND COL: logo + tagline + "Challenge Every Day." italic gradient text
- BOTTOM BAR: green system status dot + copyright

## ACCOUNT TYPE IMPACT ON HOME PAGE
- Guest: sees full page, CTAs → /auth/register
- Student (logged in): CTAs → /dashboard
- Business (logged in): CTAs → /business
- Admin (logged in): special admin badge in header nav
